WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:51.750 --> 01:53.150
I sent you tons of messages.

01:53.590 --> 01:54.500
You never replied.

01:56.270 --> 01:57.660
Why did you leave without a word?

02:02.230 --> 02:03.550
Fine, ignore my messages.

02:04.100 --> 02:05.550
I just wish I knew why.

02:23.230 --> 02:25.020
I sent you tons of messages.

02:26.230 --> 02:27.470
You never replied.

02:28.500 --> 02:29.829
Why did you leave without a word?

02:30.420 --> 02:31.140
Why?

02:37.700 --> 02:39.220
Fine, ignore my messages.

02:39.390 --> 02:40.780
I just wish I knew why.

02:42.910 --> 02:44.190
Well said.

02:44.220 --> 02:45.630
I could use this someday.

02:46.110 --> 02:47.110
Sorry.

02:47.550 --> 02:49.110
Back to business.

02:49.420 --> 02:50.990
How can you

02:51.030 --> 02:52.940
not get goosebumps

02:52.940 --> 02:54.390
when you say something so mushy?

02:54.390 --> 02:55.110
Not bad.

02:58.420 --> 02:59.500
Who's the girl?

03:12.410 --> 03:17.360
[Episode 14]
[Running Out of Brave]

03:23.060 --> 03:23.780
Gather around!

03:26.829 --> 03:27.910
Everyone.

03:27.990 --> 03:29.940
The breaststroke lesson is over.

03:30.270 --> 03:32.140
You may practice on your own.

03:32.510 --> 03:34.460
If you can't hold your breath
for too long,

03:34.700 --> 03:36.070
keep practicing.

03:36.579 --> 03:38.140
Stay safe. Class dismissed.

03:40.579 --> 03:41.670
Supervise them.

03:55.020 --> 03:57.020
Don't you owe me an explanation

03:57.790 --> 03:59.420
as to why you left without a word?

04:04.830 --> 04:06.580
Is your family giving you a hard time?

04:17.070 --> 04:18.420
What's your plan now?

04:27.420 --> 04:28.110
Sheng.

04:29.510 --> 04:30.270
What's wrong?

04:30.860 --> 04:32.140
What did you talk about?

04:34.020 --> 04:34.740
Sheng?

04:48.230 --> 04:49.110
Sheng.

04:52.180 --> 04:54.670
You're acting
like you're in an idol drama,

04:54.700 --> 04:57.070
trying to save a damsel in distress.

04:58.020 --> 05:00.510
But given her family's situation,

05:00.740 --> 05:02.550
you should stay away from her.

05:06.140 --> 05:07.510
I want to help her.

05:08.020 --> 05:08.830
What's wrong with that?

05:09.110 --> 05:09.860
Oh?

05:17.790 --> 05:18.580
Is he mad?

05:20.550 --> 05:21.420
What's his deal?

05:22.830 --> 05:24.230
See? He admitted it.

05:27.140 --> 05:27.990
Seriously?

05:29.300 --> 05:30.110
Yeah.

05:35.950 --> 05:38.350
So, why do some people go back

05:38.460 --> 05:40.030
on their own promises?

05:41.670 --> 05:42.820
It goes to show

05:43.110 --> 05:44.470
she didn't think it through

05:44.500 --> 05:45.909
when she made the promise.

05:47.030 --> 05:48.710
Why make a promise, then?

05:48.990 --> 05:50.060
Was she messing with me?

05:51.620 --> 05:52.860
Don't get so worked up.

05:53.380 --> 05:54.790
I didn't betray your trust.

05:55.230 --> 05:56.990
That's not the worst part.

05:57.670 --> 05:58.500
She won't tell me why.

06:00.150 --> 06:01.150
Relax.

06:01.550 --> 06:02.860
Qiao Qingyu avoiding you

06:02.910 --> 06:03.940
means you still have a chance.

06:04.590 --> 06:06.500
Otherwise, she could've rejected you.

06:06.620 --> 06:08.350
Obviously, she was guilt-tripped.

06:10.940 --> 06:12.670
Did I say it was Qiao Qingyu?

06:14.470 --> 06:15.260
Didn't you?

06:15.860 --> 06:16.910
It was a wild guess.

06:17.420 --> 06:19.860
By the way, when you have the time,

06:19.990 --> 06:21.030
check on your father.

06:21.940 --> 06:23.230
Just this morning,

06:23.230 --> 06:25.300
the patient's family blocked
the hospital entrance.

06:26.550 --> 06:27.820
Why should I be concerned?

06:28.060 --> 06:28.790
You know,

06:28.790 --> 06:30.150
he loves to get involved

06:30.150 --> 06:31.380
in these kinds of medical disagreements.

06:32.150 --> 06:34.230
It's different this time around.
The matter escalated.

06:34.620 --> 06:35.710
It made it to the news.

06:36.790 --> 06:37.710
Great.

06:38.230 --> 06:40.260
The world can see him
for what he really is.

07:42.940 --> 07:44.420
Did the family of the patient
in Bed 15 sign it?

07:44.670 --> 07:45.260
No.

07:47.420 --> 07:48.180
Is that so?

07:51.420 --> 07:52.230
Ming Sheng?

07:52.670 --> 07:53.110
Hey.

07:55.300 --> 07:56.180
Your father is not here.

07:57.350 --> 07:58.940
When will the surgery be over?

08:01.030 --> 08:02.420
Never mind. I can wait.

08:08.820 --> 08:10.550
Did you watch Huanzhou News?

08:16.670 --> 08:18.620
Look at this mess.

08:20.420 --> 08:21.230
You're back.

08:24.470 --> 08:25.550
I'll get another one.

08:31.300 --> 08:33.590
Mr. Chen and his wife

08:33.940 --> 08:34.990
are going on a trip.

08:35.500 --> 08:37.820
I am dog-sitting for them.

08:38.030 --> 08:38.820
See this?

08:39.230 --> 08:40.990
You must only pee on this pad.

08:43.500 --> 08:45.300
I thought keeping a dog was easy

08:45.300 --> 08:46.110
and fun.

08:47.150 --> 08:48.350
To my surprise,

08:48.470 --> 08:50.940
it's harder than taking care

08:51.470 --> 08:52.260
of a human being.

08:53.590 --> 08:54.590
I don't know

08:54.820 --> 08:56.670
what the little fella ate last night.

08:56.990 --> 08:57.990
But it made its stomach sick.

08:57.990 --> 08:59.420
It's been wreaking havoc
the whole night.

09:00.590 --> 09:02.620
None of us could get
a good night's sleep.

09:05.590 --> 09:06.500
Did you have dinner?

09:06.710 --> 09:07.620
I ordered a food delivery.

09:08.180 --> 09:09.110
Join me.

09:15.940 --> 09:18.670
Did you leave the box?

09:20.910 --> 09:23.470
I wanted you to have it
after I sorted everything.

09:23.740 --> 09:24.860
I couldn't find the time.

09:24.860 --> 09:25.860
Why?

09:26.420 --> 09:28.380
You've always hated my mom.

09:29.180 --> 09:31.150
Why did you keep an album
with photos of hers and mine?

09:32.820 --> 09:34.180
When she left the family,

09:34.500 --> 09:35.620
you weren't even five.

09:36.670 --> 09:38.300
She wasn't there to raise you,

09:38.710 --> 09:40.590
but I know

09:40.590 --> 09:42.670
how much she means to you.

09:42.740 --> 09:43.710
I thought

09:44.550 --> 09:46.230
I should keep
all your photos with her safe.

09:48.470 --> 09:50.910
I wanted to preserve them

09:51.030 --> 09:52.380
so that I could hand them to you

09:52.620 --> 09:53.740
when you were old enough.

09:55.190 --> 09:55.990
Perhaps

09:58.230 --> 10:00.950
that could make you feel like

10:03.070 --> 10:04.350
she never left

10:04.350 --> 10:06.900
but participated in your upbringing

10:06.900 --> 10:08.140
in a different way.

10:08.590 --> 10:09.470
Go on.

10:11.430 --> 10:12.590
Are you kidding me?

10:14.660 --> 10:15.590
Don't you think

10:15.590 --> 10:16.900
that it would remind me

10:17.740 --> 10:19.900
of losing my mother when I was five?

10:26.830 --> 10:27.620
Sheng.

10:28.950 --> 10:29.780
I'm sorry,

10:30.470 --> 10:31.660
especially

10:33.190 --> 10:34.950
for donating the scores

10:35.070 --> 10:36.260
your mother performed.

10:36.780 --> 10:38.230
I made a mistake.

10:38.230 --> 10:39.260
I was too careless.

10:39.260 --> 10:40.380
I should've considered your feelings.

10:40.380 --> 10:41.860
I'm not about to forgive you

10:41.860 --> 10:43.110
just because you're playing nice.

10:43.950 --> 10:45.350
If you truly cared about me,

10:45.900 --> 10:47.590
why did you chase my mom away?

10:51.310 --> 10:53.140
You will understand

10:54.500 --> 10:56.070
what happened between her and me

10:56.190 --> 10:57.470
when you are old enough.

10:57.470 --> 10:58.430
The same excuse again.

10:59.590 --> 11:00.780
It's always the same excuse.

11:00.780 --> 11:01.950
You won't tell me anything

11:01.950 --> 11:02.990
because I am too young.

11:03.500 --> 11:04.990
I am already 18.

11:05.830 --> 11:07.260
I have the right to know the truth.

11:10.350 --> 11:13.070
I am well aware

11:14.020 --> 11:15.190
of how hypocritical those excuses are.

11:15.710 --> 11:17.660
I know the high
and mighty hospital president

11:17.990 --> 11:19.140
is staying at home

11:19.830 --> 11:21.590
because of a medical dispute.

11:22.780 --> 11:24.380
You've been suspended, haven't you?

11:40.950 --> 11:41.830
Seeing you today

11:42.540 --> 11:44.310
reminds me of myself at 18.

11:45.190 --> 11:47.380
I saw the world
in an unconventional way then.

11:47.380 --> 11:48.310
Are you implying

11:48.310 --> 11:49.900
that growing up means

11:50.500 --> 11:52.230
thinking in a conventional way?

11:53.020 --> 11:53.830
No.

11:55.260 --> 11:56.350
This is when you start to have

11:56.710 --> 11:58.620
your own values.

12:00.310 --> 12:02.470
These values will determine

12:02.780 --> 12:04.950
how you see and perceive things.

12:05.710 --> 12:06.500
However,

12:06.950 --> 12:09.110
you must reach a certain age

12:09.660 --> 12:11.020
to even begin to have

12:11.310 --> 12:14.190
your own mature values.

12:14.470 --> 12:15.540
Only then

12:16.660 --> 12:17.860
will you not see things

12:17.860 --> 12:19.780
in a narrow-minded and detached way.

12:19.780 --> 12:21.500
Wait, you never told me anything.

12:22.230 --> 12:23.110
What makes you think

12:23.110 --> 12:24.590
I'd be narrow-minded?

12:25.310 --> 12:26.620
Save your breath.

12:27.350 --> 12:29.190
Spare me your fancy morality speeches.

12:31.710 --> 12:32.830
If you

12:33.590 --> 12:34.860
truly know,

12:35.830 --> 12:36.900
the patients wouldn't
have pressed charges

12:36.900 --> 12:38.620
to get you suspended.

12:51.620 --> 12:52.990
Since you can't go to work,

12:54.500 --> 12:55.990
consider this a vacation.

12:57.990 --> 12:59.430
Don't try to push yourself

13:00.380 --> 13:02.020
into doing things you're bad at,

13:03.310 --> 13:04.660
such as having a dog

13:06.830 --> 13:08.110
and being a good father.

13:22.780 --> 13:23.540
Coming.

13:27.110 --> 13:27.900
Who is it?

13:32.860 --> 13:33.660
Hello, madam.

13:34.590 --> 13:35.380
Mumu?

13:36.380 --> 13:37.230
Here for Qingyu?

13:37.230 --> 13:38.070
Yes.

13:38.310 --> 13:39.590
My family is away.

13:39.660 --> 13:41.230
I got back on my friend's bicycle.

13:41.230 --> 13:42.830
I was carrying a lot of revision files.

13:42.830 --> 13:43.710
They are quite heavy.

13:43.710 --> 13:45.500
I'm hoping Qingyu could give me a hand.

13:47.540 --> 13:49.620
They are downstairs.
We'll be right back.

13:50.540 --> 13:51.590
I'll get her.

13:51.710 --> 13:52.430
Come in.

13:52.430 --> 13:53.430
Never mind, madam.

13:55.380 --> 13:56.070
Okay.

14:08.230 --> 14:09.500
This is a concealer.

14:10.230 --> 14:11.660
Just a little bit

14:12.230 --> 14:13.950
is enough
to cover the marks on your face.

14:25.950 --> 14:26.780
Mumu.

14:28.950 --> 14:30.590
I feel awful.

14:34.500 --> 14:35.350
I know.

14:37.140 --> 14:39.350
You said you envied me for my courage.

14:42.590 --> 14:43.620
But I think

14:43.620 --> 14:45.190
I'm running out of courage.

14:47.970 --> 14:49.990
I don't even know
if everything I've done

14:52.020 --> 14:53.660
was right at all.

14:59.020 --> 15:01.830
I overestimated myself.

15:02.230 --> 15:03.710
I wanted them to admit their sins.

15:04.830 --> 15:06.110
But I was defeated.

15:08.660 --> 15:11.070
Not only did I fail to exact justice,

15:13.380 --> 15:15.230
but I also made the whole family mad.

15:20.830 --> 15:22.710
Losing doesn't mean you're wrong.

15:26.140 --> 15:28.500
The moment I was brought home,

15:28.860 --> 15:30.950
I knew what I was going to face.

15:31.740 --> 15:33.900
They could beat me, scold me,

15:33.900 --> 15:35.620
or punish me however they want.

15:37.140 --> 15:38.620
But they wanted me to apologize.

15:41.500 --> 15:42.500
I didn't do it.

15:43.990 --> 15:45.950
I didn't think I made a mistake.

15:50.350 --> 15:51.310
Someday,

15:53.470 --> 15:55.020
I'll prove them wrong.

15:57.350 --> 15:58.950
I will make them apologize to me

16:01.310 --> 16:02.740
and Qiao Beiyu.

16:07.110 --> 16:09.990
I came across a quote in a book.

16:12.620 --> 16:15.540
"Growing up is a rotten phase
everyone must go through."

16:17.990 --> 16:19.020
Perhaps growing up

16:20.950 --> 16:22.710
comes with the pain you feel.

16:28.950 --> 16:30.860
Will you be my friend forever?

16:32.660 --> 16:34.830
I will be your friend forever.

16:37.590 --> 16:38.990
I envy you.

16:40.020 --> 16:42.020
No matter how tough life becomes,

16:42.710 --> 16:43.990
you can always smile.

16:47.190 --> 16:50.470
Would you like to know
how I forget the pain?

16:51.950 --> 16:52.900
I dance.

16:55.140 --> 16:55.950
Qingyu.

16:56.780 --> 16:57.990
Join the dance club.

17:00.260 --> 17:02.860
Because of my older sister,

17:03.660 --> 17:05.710
I've always liked dancing.

17:06.140 --> 17:07.540
But my mother...

17:09.260 --> 17:10.710
If I ever get the chance,

17:10.710 --> 17:12.660
I'll fulfill her wish.

17:15.140 --> 17:18.020
Fanghao sends her to school
and picks her up after school.

17:18.470 --> 17:19.740
We installed another door

17:19.740 --> 17:21.190
and got a new lock.

17:21.540 --> 17:22.380
Don't worry.

17:22.380 --> 17:24.260
We'll keep an eye on her at all times.

17:27.540 --> 17:28.590
I know.

17:28.590 --> 17:30.020
I'll bring her back

17:30.070 --> 17:31.710
and give you an explanation.

17:33.590 --> 17:34.540
Yes.

17:34.740 --> 17:36.110
Hold on. Passing the phone to Fanghao.

17:38.230 --> 17:38.830
Dad.

17:39.710 --> 17:42.070
Qing will sit
for her mid-term exam soon.

17:43.310 --> 17:44.710
I'll keep an eye on her.

17:45.310 --> 17:46.350
She's not going anywhere.

17:49.140 --> 17:50.430
Why did you say that?

17:50.740 --> 17:51.380
Lusheng.

17:52.830 --> 17:53.780
I beg of you.

17:54.660 --> 17:55.780
Trust me on this.

17:55.950 --> 17:56.830
Beiyu is gone.

17:56.830 --> 17:57.140
Wait.

17:57.140 --> 17:58.620
We can't ruin Qing's future as well.

17:58.620 --> 17:59.380
Give me the phone.

17:59.380 --> 18:00.740
We can't let them mistreat Qing again.

18:00.740 --> 18:02.590
Call him back and explain to him!

18:04.310 --> 18:06.350
She put us all in hot water
after the stunt she pulled!

18:06.350 --> 18:07.110
She owes them

18:07.110 --> 18:08.110
an apology.

18:08.350 --> 18:10.590
They've punished her enough.

18:12.020 --> 18:12.620
Don't hang up.

18:12.620 --> 18:13.780
What else do they want?

18:15.660 --> 18:16.860
You're her father!

18:16.950 --> 18:18.950
Why won't you save your own daughter?

18:18.950 --> 18:21.020
But we can't be unreasonable.

18:21.110 --> 18:22.740
Unless we bring her back,

18:22.740 --> 18:24.660
none of us can go back
to Nanqiao Village.

18:28.580 --> 18:29.390
Li Fanghao!

18:30.430 --> 18:31.950
Listen to me.

18:32.470 --> 18:34.020
She must go back and apologize!

18:34.500 --> 18:35.430
Give me the phone!

18:37.300 --> 18:39.580
I won't let you have Qing!

18:39.740 --> 18:40.190
You're out of your mind!

18:40.190 --> 18:42.300
You are a bunch of heartless wretches!

18:42.300 --> 18:43.100
Li Fanghao!

18:52.150 --> 18:52.780
You...

18:58.870 --> 18:59.670
When

19:01.150 --> 19:03.340
you and your family
forced me to bear a son,

19:04.540 --> 19:06.100
I should've left

19:06.780 --> 19:07.950
with Bei!

19:08.670 --> 19:09.580
I should've left you

19:10.470 --> 19:11.670
and this cursed family!

19:14.190 --> 19:15.260
Stop it!

19:16.950 --> 19:18.430
I've had enough of this!

19:41.870 --> 19:43.390
You want a divorce, is that it?

19:46.580 --> 19:47.500
Qiao Lusheng...

19:48.300 --> 19:49.870
This is too much.

19:51.230 --> 19:53.260
You are a worthless coward.

19:54.390 --> 19:58.540
You can't even say
you want a divorce out loud!

20:07.630 --> 20:08.950
Grandpa called.

20:08.950 --> 20:10.260
They want you to apologize.

20:12.870 --> 20:14.100
Mom found out

20:14.100 --> 20:16.230
you'd be in for a harsh beating
if you went back.

20:16.340 --> 20:17.470
She refused to send you back.

20:18.990 --> 20:20.740
Mom and Dad have been
fighting all night.

20:22.670 --> 20:24.710
Qiao Beiyu's miscarriage

20:24.710 --> 20:26.230
was nothing more than a rumor.

20:26.470 --> 20:27.670
But thanks to you,

20:28.300 --> 20:30.430
it was proven to be true.

20:30.670 --> 20:31.820
There are all kinds of theories online

20:31.820 --> 20:34.260
about how Qiao Beiyu died.

20:34.990 --> 20:36.580
Jinrui got a divorce,

20:37.100 --> 20:38.500
but he hasn't told Grandma.

20:39.580 --> 20:40.390
I heard

20:41.230 --> 20:43.260
Aunt Yanfen was so upset
that she ended up in the hospital.

20:43.580 --> 20:45.230
Our parents are getting a divorce.

20:46.740 --> 20:48.990
I never wanted things to get this ugly.

20:50.870 --> 20:52.340
Your intention is good.

20:52.780 --> 20:54.950
You wanted to avenge Beiyu.

20:55.910 --> 20:57.670
But now, you've failed to avenge her

20:58.340 --> 21:00.100
while tearing this family apart.

21:01.190 --> 21:03.190
We knew Beiyu was the victim.

21:03.190 --> 21:04.780
How could we pretend nothing happened?

21:08.430 --> 21:09.300
I don't know.

21:11.390 --> 21:13.060
But please, don't be stubborn.

21:14.060 --> 21:15.060
It will never be over

21:15.060 --> 21:17.300
until you apologize to their family.

21:18.150 --> 21:20.060
Qiao Beiyu is gone,

21:20.300 --> 21:21.950
but life goes on.

21:23.060 --> 21:23.990
Just think of this

21:25.060 --> 21:27.340
as brushing them off.

21:27.630 --> 21:28.540
An apology from you

21:28.630 --> 21:30.340
will make things easier for our family.

21:30.340 --> 21:31.260
Is that too much to ask?

22:43.950 --> 22:45.020
Dad, stop drinking.

22:45.060 --> 22:46.230
It's bad for your health.

22:53.740 --> 22:55.390
If you could be more sensible

22:55.820 --> 22:57.150
and stop upsetting me,

22:58.390 --> 23:00.020
I might live a few years longer.

23:05.740 --> 23:07.230
Believe it or not,

23:07.710 --> 23:08.870
I never wanted everyone

23:08.870 --> 23:10.100
to suffer this much.

23:11.540 --> 23:12.780
Everyone is suffering now.

23:15.390 --> 23:16.430
Your mom is suffering.

23:17.430 --> 23:18.430
I'm suffering.

23:19.670 --> 23:21.910
You are tearing this family apart!

23:25.150 --> 23:26.580
What are you thinking?

23:32.020 --> 23:33.230
I'll go with you.

23:34.780 --> 23:36.390
I'll go back to Nanqiao Village.

23:39.670 --> 23:41.500
You got us into big trouble.

23:42.150 --> 23:43.300
Your grandparents,

23:43.990 --> 23:45.020
your uncle, and your aunt,

23:45.020 --> 23:46.820
they won't go easy on you.

23:49.470 --> 23:53.100
Going back to the village means misery.

23:53.230 --> 23:54.500
What else can we do?

23:55.190 --> 23:57.020
Everyone thinks I'm in the wrong.

23:57.260 --> 23:58.740
Fine, I'll take the responsibility.

24:00.540 --> 24:02.100
I don't care how they punish me.

24:02.100 --> 24:03.020
I'm not afraid.

24:03.780 --> 24:04.710
But I can't stand it

24:04.710 --> 24:05.990
if you fight with Mom all the time.

24:05.990 --> 24:07.020
Fine.

24:08.780 --> 24:10.020
You're the mature one.

24:16.340 --> 24:17.740
We'll leave tomorrow morning.

24:18.300 --> 24:19.500
Don't tell your mom.

24:26.500 --> 24:28.150
Wear something thick tomorrow.

24:51.470 --> 24:53.780
This is all my doing.
The blame is on me.

24:54.150 --> 24:55.990
It's too late to undo anything.

24:56.820 --> 24:58.470
But I alone am responsible.

24:59.580 --> 25:00.990
Grandpa, punish me any way you want.

25:00.990 --> 25:02.990
You ruined my son's life!

25:04.820 --> 25:06.100
He is only in his 20s.

25:06.540 --> 25:08.470
You destroyed his future!

25:09.740 --> 25:10.820
I will never hurt this family

25:10.820 --> 25:11.950
in the future.

25:11.950 --> 25:13.300
In the future?

25:13.540 --> 25:15.340
The whole village knows

25:15.470 --> 25:16.910
Jinrui was adopted.

25:17.020 --> 25:18.300
Is your mom too scared to come here?

25:18.740 --> 25:20.340
Are you even here to apologize?

25:20.340 --> 25:22.540
You never even shed a tear!

25:23.060 --> 25:23.950
Lusheng.

25:24.540 --> 25:27.910
Make sure you teach her a lesson today.

25:28.100 --> 25:29.150
Beat her!

25:31.630 --> 25:32.340
Lusheng!

25:34.580 --> 25:35.630
Do it now!

25:39.230 --> 25:39.820
Dad...

25:40.630 --> 25:41.540
Are you doing it or not?

25:41.910 --> 25:42.910
Do it!

25:44.340 --> 25:45.990
Do it now!

25:51.990 --> 25:52.390
Dad!

25:52.780 --> 25:55.580
Dad! Dad!

25:55.870 --> 25:58.020
Dad! Calm down!

26:00.430 --> 26:01.020
Dad.

26:17.260 --> 26:17.820
Mom!

26:20.390 --> 26:21.020
Dad.

26:22.820 --> 26:23.630
Haisheng,

26:24.580 --> 26:25.390
Yanfen.

26:27.580 --> 26:29.060
Qingyu is young and rash.

26:30.540 --> 26:32.060
She hazed Jinrui's wedding

26:32.820 --> 26:34.060
and embarrassed you.

26:35.710 --> 26:36.870
She did wrong.

26:38.630 --> 26:39.910
But she is just a child.

26:40.710 --> 26:41.580
You can blame me

26:42.910 --> 26:44.390
for not restrain her

26:45.390 --> 26:46.630
as her mother.

26:46.820 --> 26:47.390
Mom...

26:49.430 --> 26:50.990
As long as it appeases you,

26:53.060 --> 26:54.670
you may beat me or scold me

26:54.710 --> 26:56.100
however you like.

26:57.340 --> 26:59.020
I apologize to you.

26:59.670 --> 27:00.390
Mom!

27:01.540 --> 27:02.950
Stand up.

27:03.740 --> 27:04.990
An apology?

27:05.870 --> 27:07.470
With some fancy excuses?

27:08.300 --> 27:10.060
You two daughters

27:10.060 --> 27:11.300
destroyed my son.

27:11.580 --> 27:12.710
The damage you cause Jinrui

27:12.710 --> 27:14.580
will last a lifetime!

27:14.580 --> 27:16.300
A lifetime! Do you hear me?

27:16.910 --> 27:18.060
Calm down.

27:24.780 --> 27:25.580
Yanfen.

27:26.870 --> 27:28.780
Let's ask our conscience.

27:30.230 --> 27:32.430
We may have destroyed Jinrui's life,

27:34.260 --> 27:35.500
but what about my Beiyu?

27:37.910 --> 27:39.260
I lost my Beiyu.

27:45.780 --> 27:46.630
Beiyu?

27:47.540 --> 27:50.020
Her death has nothing to do with Jinrui.

27:50.020 --> 27:51.340
She had it coming.

27:51.430 --> 27:52.540
She deserved it!

27:52.540 --> 27:54.230
She deserved to die!

28:05.260 --> 28:07.230
Qingyu, stand up.

28:09.230 --> 28:09.820
Stand.

28:17.150 --> 28:18.630
Do as I say.

28:31.230 --> 28:32.020
Yanfen.

28:34.950 --> 28:36.470
Let me tell you another secret.

28:37.540 --> 28:38.340
It was me

28:39.670 --> 28:40.950
who told Qingyu to do it.

28:41.740 --> 28:43.020
Mom!

28:47.540 --> 28:49.060
I'll make you pay!

28:49.430 --> 28:50.540
How could you still defend Qingyu?

28:50.540 --> 28:51.710
You'll pay for this!

28:51.710 --> 28:52.260
Yanfen!

28:52.430 --> 28:53.230
That's enough!

28:53.390 --> 28:54.230
Let go of me!

28:55.230 --> 28:56.540
I'll make you pay!

28:57.260 --> 28:58.390
You'll pay for this!

28:58.430 --> 29:00.670
You and your daughters
are cursed fiends!

29:00.780 --> 29:01.780
We've had enough trouble!

29:01.780 --> 29:03.190
Stop spewing nonsense!

29:03.580 --> 29:04.390
Yanfen!

29:04.390 --> 29:06.390
Dad!

29:06.390 --> 29:09.990
We deserve justice, Dad!

29:14.020 --> 29:14.670
Mom!

29:16.260 --> 29:17.710
Mom, what are you doing?

29:17.910 --> 29:18.710
Mom!

29:19.780 --> 29:20.390
Mom!

29:22.430 --> 29:23.340
Stop hitting yourself!

29:27.230 --> 29:27.780
Mom!

29:33.300 --> 29:33.910
Mom!

29:34.580 --> 29:35.150
Mom!

29:37.630 --> 29:38.540
Stop hitting yourself!

29:46.190 --> 29:47.390
Let's leave.

29:47.500 --> 29:48.710
Come with me.

30:01.460 --> 30:04.410
[Wedding]

30:18.230 --> 30:21.060
The whole family is in pieces,
thanks to you.

31:43.020 --> 31:44.470
I'll wash the vegetables.

32:18.100 --> 32:20.100
How were we going to resolve it
without her apology?

32:21.060 --> 32:23.020
My family will never stop
coming after us.

32:23.020 --> 32:25.190
I had it all planned out.

32:25.190 --> 32:26.540
She was supposed to apologize

32:26.540 --> 32:28.190
and get some punishment.

32:28.190 --> 32:29.820
It wouldn't have taken too long.

32:29.820 --> 32:31.820
Her grandpa wouldn't harm her.

32:32.470 --> 32:33.390
But you?

32:33.390 --> 32:35.260
You just made things so much worse.

32:36.580 --> 32:38.430
What was going on in your mind?

32:42.870 --> 32:45.190
I lost my mind, thanks to your family.

33:10.950 --> 33:11.670
Hey.

33:12.670 --> 33:13.990
With all due respect,

33:15.820 --> 33:16.910
I think

33:17.670 --> 33:21.060
Dad and Grandpa weren't wrong.

33:23.780 --> 33:25.630
It's true that Jinrui hurt Beiyu.

33:25.990 --> 33:27.910
Grandpa and the family kept it a secret.

33:27.990 --> 33:29.990
Even if they've all done
the wrong thing,

33:30.020 --> 33:31.820
and they must pay for their wrongdoing,

33:33.990 --> 33:35.060
but this is

33:35.340 --> 33:37.060
too big of a price to pay.

33:38.740 --> 33:39.540
If

33:41.470 --> 33:42.150
you knew

33:42.150 --> 33:44.260
things would turn out this way,

33:46.390 --> 33:48.230
would you still avenge Beiyu

33:48.540 --> 33:50.230
the same way?

33:57.060 --> 33:58.740
I'll stay in the dorm
starting this semester.

34:00.100 --> 34:01.340
Our parents are always fighting.

34:01.870 --> 34:03.430
You're always putting on a long face.

34:04.230 --> 34:05.580
I can't study in this house.

35:41.540 --> 35:43.060
Take a bite.

35:43.350 --> 35:46.180
You need to grow strong so you can fly.

35:46.390 --> 35:47.430
Eat up.

35:48.430 --> 35:48.870
Eat up.

36:07.060 --> 36:07.990
Eat your food.

36:25.430 --> 36:26.100
Qingyu.

36:27.830 --> 36:29.580
I know you don't want to talk to me.

36:30.580 --> 36:33.180
But please listen to me.

36:35.270 --> 36:36.470
I know you hate

36:36.470 --> 36:38.020
this family.

36:39.470 --> 36:42.020
Honestly, I hate it too.

36:42.310 --> 36:43.910
But you are still too young

36:43.910 --> 36:45.430
to live outside on your own.

36:46.390 --> 36:47.790
You will get mistreated.

36:50.750 --> 36:51.870
Bear

36:52.700 --> 36:53.830
with it.

36:54.870 --> 36:57.540
When you get old enough, graduate,

36:57.950 --> 36:59.990
and contribute to society,

37:00.180 --> 37:02.100
you can do whatever you want.

37:02.390 --> 37:03.660
I won't interfere.

37:07.350 --> 37:08.540
Please trust me on this.

37:09.660 --> 37:12.910
I am a person of my word.

37:35.140 --> 37:37.020
How much money do you have
on the meal card?

37:37.350 --> 37:39.220
Enough for a term.

37:39.500 --> 37:42.060
Get decent meals.
Don't try to save money.

37:42.990 --> 37:45.430
Take a ten-minute nap at noon.

37:45.430 --> 37:47.020
Madam, Qingyu.

37:47.750 --> 37:48.540
Hello, madam.

37:48.750 --> 37:49.430
Hi.

37:49.620 --> 37:51.060
Wait here tonight.

37:51.060 --> 37:51.660
Hmm.

37:51.750 --> 37:52.790
Qingyu and I will go in.

37:52.790 --> 37:53.270
Okay.

37:56.540 --> 37:58.500
She worries too much.

37:59.540 --> 38:01.390
She is too overbearing,

38:01.540 --> 38:03.500
but I know she means well.

38:12.620 --> 38:14.500
I should stop upsetting them.

38:14.950 --> 38:16.310
Since I can't change the past,

38:16.750 --> 38:18.270
I'll just behave from now on.

38:33.270 --> 38:34.660
Does it stick?

38:48.220 --> 38:49.020
What's up?

38:49.540 --> 38:50.100
It's nothing.

38:50.100 --> 38:51.270
Show me!

38:54.270 --> 38:55.140
What's the deal with you?

38:56.180 --> 38:57.790
Oops, you sat on the glue.

38:57.790 --> 38:58.390
Oh boy.

38:58.390 --> 39:00.140
You got a taste of your own poison.

39:00.620 --> 39:02.100
You had it coming for being a bully.

39:02.540 --> 39:03.270
Says the big bullies

39:03.270 --> 39:04.950
of the school.

39:05.390 --> 39:06.750
Drop the act.

39:06.910 --> 39:07.700
Why?

39:07.750 --> 39:09.700
Can't we have a change of heart

39:09.700 --> 39:10.500
and start anew?

39:10.500 --> 39:11.270
Yeah.

39:11.660 --> 39:13.140
So, stop being a bully,

39:13.180 --> 39:15.020
or we'll punish you
in the name of justice.

39:15.660 --> 39:16.790
Let's go to the toilet.

39:28.430 --> 39:29.540
Hand it over.

40:17.350 --> 40:19.700
Someone wants you to have this.

40:27.660 --> 40:31.060
[If you turn around,
I'll always be there.]

40:51.620 --> 40:52.350
Sheng!

40:53.140 --> 40:53.750
Hey.

40:54.390 --> 40:55.700
Carry on.

41:00.990 --> 41:01.870
I passed her the note.

41:01.910 --> 41:02.830
What did she say?

41:03.390 --> 41:04.350
Nothing at all.

41:05.910 --> 41:06.950
How did she react?

41:07.500 --> 41:08.470
No reactions.

41:08.470 --> 41:09.540
Nothing?

41:10.990 --> 41:11.790
Yeah.

41:12.500 --> 41:13.390
She reacted.

41:15.430 --> 41:16.790
She gave it a long thought.

41:16.910 --> 41:18.270
A long thought?

41:22.910 --> 41:25.020
What is that supposed to mean?

41:37.830 --> 41:39.540
Oh, Qiao Qingyu.

41:39.830 --> 41:41.700
Seeing you reminds me of something.

41:41.700 --> 41:43.580
A few days ago, I saw Ming Sheng

41:43.580 --> 41:45.220
getting out of a cab with a girl.

41:45.220 --> 41:46.430
Was it you?

41:47.950 --> 41:49.580
Was she staying

41:49.620 --> 41:50.910
at Ming Sheng's grandpa's?

42:23.150 --> 42:26.840
♪Perhaps♪

42:27.350 --> 42:33.050
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

42:34.190 --> 42:39.590
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

42:40.590 --> 42:46.150
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

42:51.820 --> 42:55.490
♪In the future♪

42:55.950 --> 43:01.670
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

43:03.170 --> 43:08.240
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

43:09.490 --> 43:14.650
♪That never expires♪

43:18.250 --> 43:22.720
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

43:23.720 --> 43:27.390
♪Is your name♪

43:27.890 --> 43:32.990
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

43:34.070 --> 43:37.290
♪At first sight♪

43:37.720 --> 43:41.000
♪The future has been determined♪

43:41.690 --> 43:47.250
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

43:48.350 --> 43:51.890
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

43:52.350 --> 43:56.290
♪Is a place♪

43:56.590 --> 44:02.150
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

44:02.820 --> 44:06.190
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

44:06.520 --> 44:09.990
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

44:10.520 --> 44:16.590
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
